Company Overview of Bel Air Investment Advisors LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Bel Air Investment Advisors LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals. It also caters to individuals, pension and profit sharing plans, pooled investment vehicles, charitable organizations, and corporations. The firm manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. The firm also makes alternative investments. It primarily invests in growth and value stocks of small-cap, mid-cap, and large-cap companies. For its fixed income securities, the firm invests in tax-free or taxable bonds and municipal bonds. It employs quantitative a...
Bel Air Investment Advisors LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals. It also caters to individuals, pension and profit sharing plans, pooled investment vehicles, charitable organizations, and corporations. The firm manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. The firm also makes alternative investments. It primarily invests in growth and value stocks of small-cap, mid-cap, and large-cap companies. For its fixed income securities, the firm invests in tax-free or taxable bonds and municipal bonds. It employs quantitative and qualitative analysis to make its investments. Bel Air Investment Advisors LLC was founded in 1997 and is based in Los Angeles, California with an additional office in San Francisco, California. Bel Air Investment Advisors LLC operates as a subsidiary of Fiera US Holding Inc.
