Bel Air Investment Advisors LLC



















 




Bel Air Investment Advisors LLC (Bel Air), widely respected in the U.S. investment community, was founded in 1997 as an independent wealth management firm. In 2013, Bel Air was acquired by the Fiera Capital Corporation and is now a leading member of the Fiera Capital group of Companies. Distinctly known for its national presence and expertise in the delivery of a premier client service model, Bel Air provides customized management services and investment counsel exclusively to high net worth individuals, families, and foundations with $20 million or more in investable assets.
Bel Air distinguishes itself through its diverse mix of "best-in-class" proprietary and sub-advisory investment strategies within its open architecture platform. The firm's leading investment advisors, some with over 35 years of investment experience, oversee and manage approximately $7 billion in assets and have navigated industry fluctuations and diverse market conditions. They have repeatedly demonstrated their ability to cater to specific client needs and preferences, in virtually every situation.
Bel Air advisors' keen understanding, objectivity, comprehensive knowledge and integrated experience in the market, are key in identifying and selecting the most appropriate investment options for each of their clients' and in protecting and preserving their wealth.
